\pc \bdit Ninafurahi Ananipenda, Yesu Mwokozi Ananipenda; Ninafurahi Ananipenda, Ananipenda mimi.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Wimbo mumoja tu nitamwimbia Nitakapomutazama Mupendwa, Nitamwimbia Mwokozi milele\bd*\bd :\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd “\bd*\bd Ulinipenda \bd*\bd –\bd*\bd  ajabu la kweli\bd*\bd ”\bd*
